verses.verse: O praise <WH1984> <WH8761> the YY <WH3068>, all ye nations <WH1471>: praise <WH7623> <WH8761> him, all ye people <WH523>.
For his merciful <WH2617> kindness <WH2617> is great <WH1396> <WH8804> toward us: and the truth <WH571> of the YY <WH3068> endureth for ever <WH5769>. Praise <WH1984> <WH8761> ye the YY <WH3050>.
